helpful: 1 of 2 people (50%) found this review helpful
review: Before my review for this game was negative but then the glitch where i could not save was fixed and now I do highly recommend this game to people who like to play sandbox games and crafting games, there is also a very unique building system because you have to be aware of water pressure or else the base could start to break down and flood and you have to watch out for how much power you have if you want your machines to work within the base its a fun unique game and I highly recommend it.
